           &mt LSHFT LC(A)  &kp LEFT   &kp DOWN      &kp RIGHT        &kp LC(F)    &trans    &kp NUMBER_4  &kp N5        &kp NUMBER_6  &trans
&kp SPACE  &kp LC(Z)        &kp LC(X)  &kp LC(C)     &kp LC(V)        &kp LC(Y)    &kp N0    &kp N1        &kp NUMBER_2  &kp NUMBER_3  &kp MINUS  &trans
